OL,3,CLearner driver 'anxious and
OL,4,Cfrustrated' due to lack of driving
OL,5,Ctests
OL,7,FA learner driver says she feels
OL,8,Fanxious and frustrated due to the lack
OL,9,Fof availability in driving tests.
OL,11,FSiobhan Routledge, from Aldershot,
OL,12,FHampshire, had her last driving test
OL,13,Fin November 2023 and failed due to the
OL,14,Famount of pressure she felt to pass.
OL,16,FShe has been taking lessons for nearly
OL,17,Ftwo years and has not been able to
OL,18,Ffind any tests in centres close to her.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/9
