OL,7,FSince this, she has rebooked a test
OL,8,Ffourteen months after her first
OL,9,Fattempt, in Crawley, Sussex, over an
OL,10,Fhour drive away.
OL,12,FSiobhan said: "There are loads of
OL,13,Fpeople in my situation, some in even
OL,14,Fworse circumstances than me.
OL,16,F"You have to rely on cancellations,
OL,17,Fbut when someone has a test, they are
OL,18,Fgoing to want to keep it"
