OL,7,FSiobhan fears that her personal life
OL,8,Fand career have taken a back seat, as
OL,9,Fnot being able to drive has affected
OL,10,Fwhat she is able to do.
OL,12,F"It is restricting me from doing a lot
OL,13,Fmore in my career because I want to go
OL,14,Fout and do more wedding and event
OL,15,Fhair, and I cannot do that because I
OL,16,Fcannot drive," she said
