OL,7,F"I have a wedding booked in a couple
OL,8,Fof weeks but I have got to get the
OL,9,Ftrain there and someone from the
OL,10,Fwedding has got to pick me up from the
OL,11,Fstation, which is an inconvenience to
OL,12,Fthem.
OL,14,F"People say 'just get a bus, train or
OL,15,Fwalk', but bus and transport fares are
OL,16,Fridiculous prices, and it would end up
OL,17,Fthat half of my wages would go onto
OL,18,Fthat."
