OL,3,CLearner driver 'anxious and
OL,4,Cfrustrated' due to lack of driving
OL,5,Ctests
OL,7,FIn 2020, statistics from RAC show that
OL,8,Fonly 220,000 people passed their
OL,9,Fdriving test, compared to the 750,000
OL,10,Fwho pass on a regular year.
OL,12,FBecause of this, the DVSA are playing
OL,13,Fcatch up to get through the backlog,
OL,14,Fwhich included administering 2 million
OL,15,Ftests in 2023.
OL,17,FHowever, this has led to test touters
OL,18,Fwho use bots to scroll through booking
OL,19,Fsystem as soon as tests go live,
OL,20,Fsnapping up the tests and selling them
OL,21,Fon for up to #200.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/9
