OL,5,Ctests
OL,7,FWith this, DVSA have been working to
OL,8,Fshut down these businesses, having
OL,9,Fclosed over 700.
OL,11,FPeter Swallow, MP for Bracknell, led a
OL,12,Fdebate in Parliament on Driving Test
OL,13,FDelays and the shortage of test
OL,14,Fcentres for people to be able to take
OL,15,Ftheir test.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/9
