OL,3,CLearner driver 'anxious and
OL,4,Cfrustrated' due to lack of driving
OL,5,Ctests
OL,7,FHis constituency doesn't have a
OL,8,Ftesting centre, and is a town of
OL,9,F120,000 people, so hopeful students
OL,10,Fhave to travel to Reading and
OL,11,FFarnborough to find their next closest
OL,12,Fsite, with Slough and Chertsey not far
OL,13,Fbehind them
OL,15,FMP Peter Swallow, said: "It is a
OL,16,Fmassive issue. We all remember that
OL,17,Ffeeling of liberation and freedom of
OL,18,Fpassing our test - but that is being
OL,19,Ftaken away for so many young people.
OL,20,FThey are waiting far too long to get a
OL,21,Ftest.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/9
