OL,7,F"I have to keep a space available for
OL,8,Fthem in six months time but in the
OL,9,Fmeantime, I have to replace them so it
OL,10,Fcan create a bit of an issue with us
OL,11,Fpotentially being overloaded with
OL,12,Fpotential pupils.
OL,14,F"From the pupils point of view, it's
OL,15,Fvery frustrating to try and get the
OL,16,Ftest, number one, and it can affect
OL,17,Ftheir employment, their access to
OL,18,Fcollege."
